# Docker Secrets Audit Log
#
# Purpose: Track all secret usage, validation, and rotation events
# Format: [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS] EVENT_TYPE: SECRET_NAME | field1=value1 | field2=value2 | status=success|failed
# Location: docker/secrets-audit.log
#
# Cleanup: Archive and compress monthly:
#   mv docker/secrets-audit.log docker/secrets-audit.log.$(date +%Y-%m-%d)
#   gzip docker/secrets-audit.log.*
#   find docker/ -name "secrets-audit.log.*" -mtime +90 -delete
#
# NOTE: This is an append-only log. Do not edit manually.
# Entry format: [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS] EVENT_TYPE: SECRET_NAME | field1=value1 | status=success|failed|warning
#
# Event Types:
# - SETUP: Initial setup of .env file
# - VALIDATION_PASSED: Secret validation succeeded
# - VALIDATION_FAILED: Secret validation failed
# - ROTATED: Secret was rotated
# - USED: Secret was accessed by service
# - INCIDENT: Security incident (compromise, unauthorized access, etc.)
#
# Example entries:
# [2026-03-18 14:23:45] ROTATED: GITHUB_TOKEN | old_hash=abc123... | new_hash=xyz789... | status=success
# [2026-03-18 14:25:00] VALIDATION_FAILED: RESEND_API_KEY | reason=empty | status=failed
# [2026-03-18 14:26:15] USED: GITHUB_TOKEN | service=github-official | result=success
# [2026-03-18 14:30:00] SETUP: Initial .env configuration | secrets_count=5 | status=success
#

